Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.35,0:00:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.87,0:00:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you fooling around for?!
