Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.95,0:00:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Audition?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.11,0:00:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.78,0:00:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.69,0:00:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you can't transform her...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can't help her go to the audition!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't want to say this, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You and that girl...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.12,0:01:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...are somehow seem to be related.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.59,0:01:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you get any closer to her...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.12,0:01:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it'll bring back your memories from when you were a human.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:08.63,0:01:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know what will happen then, right?!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.43,0:01:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I love you...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:19.64,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to be with you forever...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.65,0:01:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't want you to become a ghost, Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.23,0:01:36.24,Episode Title,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(330,340)\bord2.5}Run! To the Audition!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:52.18,0:01:53.83,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm so tired...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.83,0:01:56.16,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going to rest for a bit...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The whistle's missing...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.15,0:02:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.47,0:02:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't call for Takuto without it...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.58,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't want you to become a ghost, Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:26.67,0:02:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madam...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.66,0:02:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It doesn't look like she's in the house.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.35,0:02:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madam!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm fine...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.55,0:02:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was feeling a little dizzy...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For heaven's sake...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How much more is she going to make me worry?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Running away from the hospital in her state...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hospital?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did she collapse?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\an8}Madam.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.15,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\an8}Please rest.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\an8}You have to watch your health.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.79,0:03:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.91,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't let you go... even if it kills me.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I mean...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I just gave you a serious confession...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.84,0:03:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it's the fifty-seventh time.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.97,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Gah!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No matter...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:23.56,0:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No matter how many times I confess...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.32,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'm always serious! {Seriously, now's not the time for your bs}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto, you insensitive jerk!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It hurts!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.77,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.25,0:03:49.14,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto's worrying about me?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It hurts so much that I can't stand...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.25,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, you're a tough person...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You should be able to handle this.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.00,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.59,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What do you mean, "I'm tough?!"
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So you are fine, after all.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.22,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Damn it...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.18,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If it's come to this...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.58,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My final trick...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.60,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you aren't going to listen to my advice...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'll report everything that's happened to the Shinigami main office.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You'll be punished.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No matter what the handbook tells you...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No matter what the Shinigami main office will do to me...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I have to go.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why do you go that far for her?! {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't even know that myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I can't just leave her alone!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If she can't sing...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.06,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I get this feeling that she'd die from that alone!
