Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Dr. Wakaouji.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did someone from her home call?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The housekeeper, Tanaka-san, did just a moment ago...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.44,0:05:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She hasn't gone home yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That girl...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She lost the whistle?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I might have an idea.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going to look right now.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx85\fscy85}Please let me know if something happens.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90\an8}Today's a sunny day, just like yesterday.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90\an8}It looks like it'll be this summer's hottest day yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90\an8}Well, next up is the traffic report.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90\an8}Let's ask Kawada-san from the traffic center.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90\an8}Kawada-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:06.37,0:06:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90\an8}Yes!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.48,0:06:17.37,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... fell asleep out here?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.58,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's cold...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.56,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto isn't coming...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.96,0:06:35.60,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I probably can't make it now...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.65,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.66,0:06:44.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The moon... you know...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.91,0:06:47.43,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We can only see one side from the earth.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Such a beautiful moon...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.18,0:06:57.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... on the other side... there are lots of craters left by meteorites.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It hides its wounds and keeps on smiling.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The first time I met you...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.22,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I thought your name fit perfectly.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't cry.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.34,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't cry... until I see you again.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.55,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If she ran away from the hospital...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.03,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...there's only one place she could have gone.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.03,0:07:33.26,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She has to be where the audition is being held!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She didn't get on, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.82,Note,,0,0,0,Sign,{\be1\bord0\shad0\c&HF1C77A&\fscx120\fscy130\move(320,178,320,425,25,1694)\frx18\fry0}Next Stop: The Park
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.82,Note,,0,0,0,Sign,{\be1\bord0\shad0\c&HA36F23&\move(138,0,138,245,25,1694)}{\p1}(m 179 219 l 183 184 247 175 311 175 421 179 451 181 453 220)}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.17,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,Sign,{No TS?}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning, Madoka-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you so much for yesterday.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I had such a great time!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I did too.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You looked good yesterday, Madoka-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going to do my best today!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm looking forward to this!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Shall we start the camera test?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.07,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\an8}Then... Madoka-san... {split}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\an8}This way please.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Answer the phone, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.97,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.38,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Which way should I go?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.88,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't move anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh no.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong with this girl?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's probably for a TV show.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They do this all the time lately.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All those variety shows...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.38,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.59,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wasn't a good girl...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.45,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You must all be worried since I ran away from the hospital...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.72,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It looks like I won't make it to the audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.21,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.59,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.32,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.40,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fad(0,400)}Even though you helped me so much...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Besides...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.46,0:09:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...still haven't apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:12.67,Myself Romaji ED2 (Ep 18 Faint),,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}Doushite doushite suki nandarou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:12.67,Myself TL(Pre-Credits),,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:18.88,Myself Romaji ED2 (Ep 18 Faint),,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(200,150)}Konna ni namida afureteru
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:18.88,Myself TL(Pre-Credits),,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(200,150)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.31,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.41,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All I wanted was to sing...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.19,0:10:35.09,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun... I wanted just to see you...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!!!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hold on!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She isn't breathing.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.00,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.44,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please... open your eyes!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.10,0:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun? {Baka}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.52,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.05,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just now... Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you doing... falling asleep in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... um...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This way!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... hey! You! Hold it!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:43.99,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.83,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.53,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... no... it doesn't hurt anywhere now.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.07,0:12:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.38,0:12:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When does the audition start?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's already 11 o'clock?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What should I do?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The audition's already started!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hurry up.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We can still make it.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:05.00,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You want Eichi to notice you, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can't give up, then!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.94,0:13:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You think I'll let you get there on time?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Absolutely not...!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah? {Oh no}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.84,0:13:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?! {Here it comes}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kya!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't look! {Poor Mitsuki}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}H-Hurry up and get away from there.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My shoe's stuck... I can't get away!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.01,0:13:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't look!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry, did that hurt?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez... Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.46,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're almost there.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm just getting started... {edited}
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.25,0:14:25.92,Notice 01 (Episode 18),,0,0,0,Sign,{\blur0.6\frz3.16\fscx109\fscy153\pos(102,77)\clip(m 73 53 l 129 51 131 101 74 103)}Warning!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.25,0:14:25.92,Notice 01 (Episode 18),,0,0,0,Sign,{\blur0.6\frz3.16\fscx131\fscy143\pos(102,107)\clip(m 73 90 l 129 89 130 137 76 141)}Glass!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just look at her face...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:29.35,0:14:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.89,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why am I seeing stars all around? {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah... somehow...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah..?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way! {Abunai ja nai ka?! Meroko no Baka!}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.04,0:14:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.13,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... that was close...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}O-Oh crap.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if this is for TV too?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They do a lot of filming these days, huh...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Too easy.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.97,0:15:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscy110\fscx110}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscy110\fscx110}It's {\i1}Full Moon{\i0} !
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.86,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscy110\fscx110}{\i1}Full Moon's{\i0}  right here!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.28,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0} ?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:29.82,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really? The real thing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon {\i0}?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then the filming just now...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.25,0:15:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There she is!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-What do I do?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's run!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This way!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.93,0:15:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}An idol couldn't possibly be here... {idol diving, it's the latest craze}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We should still make sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Somehow... we managed to lose them...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.28,0:16:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.99,0:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The studio is in that building!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.15,0:16:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Over there!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's going in the building!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Crap... they found us!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:35.02,0:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What a relief...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... s-sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.11,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... that was...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.43,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Was that... my first kiss? {It is if you want it to be}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:58.08,0:17:01.91,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... it wasn't gentle at all...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry that it wasn't from someone else.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.47,0:17:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's your fault for collapsing in the first place... that's why I had to use mouth-to-mouth...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't have to put it like that...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well... don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It was only just mouth-to-mouth...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.53,0:17:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That... wasn't... a kiss...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It doesn't count as a first kiss.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.91,0:17:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It stopped...?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why now?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We were almost there.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.38,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko's doing, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no way a Half-Shinigami can beat me.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.90,0:18:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.15,0:18:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I asked you something you didn't want to hear...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways... don't give up.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.72,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Didn't you decide that you were going to do your best until Eichi noticed you?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:17.32,0:18:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... I won't make it there in time now...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll get you there in time.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you want to rat me out to the \NShinigami main office, go ahead!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.26,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going to help her, no matter what happens!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You got that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.94,0:18:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So pretty...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:00.79,0:19:03.37,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even if they're just replicas...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.99,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...they're really beautiful, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can go the rest of the way by yourself, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.48,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:25.28,0:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:25.94,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Go for it.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:26.81,0:19:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We will be announcing our decision now.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.49,0:19:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The image character for Mermaid Tear is...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Wakamatsu Madoka-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:34.52,0:21:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That girl...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She didn't make it in time for the audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That means that I accomplished my mission, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dailogue,{\be1}Not at all!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't everything okay now?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.16,0:21:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't have to go around \Nprotecting that girl anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No! Not yet!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm not going to just let her run away!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.77,0:21:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't let her give up on singing that easily!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Next time on Full Moon wo Sagashite:
Dialogue: 2,0:21:59.72,0:22:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The Voice of Song that Can't Reach Him
Dialogue: 2,0:22:01.47,0:22:02.86,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look forward to it!
