Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:49.91,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,100)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:56.38,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\be3\fad(200,200)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:27.53,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(166,100)}I lost way too much back then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:31.83,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I couldn't sing at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:36.29,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}That place you had to leave for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:43.93,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}It happened to be the place where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:50.27,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}On that day I could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:55.15,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}The desolation lying in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:21:00.73,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I wonder if it's the same for both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:08.16,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}If you would just notice, I'm always by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:14.21,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:20.21,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:26.30,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}I never knew what was supporting me, back then, and even now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:32.85,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,840)}Until we became so far apart...
